data.description: Experience the luxurious comfort of this remarkable end unit condo that's a true oasis of tranquility. When you step inside this unit, and you'll be welcomed by the soaring vaulted ceilings, which not only creates an open and airy atmosphere but also a primary suite on each level giving you the feeling of spaciousness that's hard to find elsewhere. As you explore further, you'll find the heart of this home—the newly renovated kitchen. It's not just a kitchen; it's a culinary haven. Adorned with elegant granite countertops and pristine white cabinets, it's a place where your culinary creations will come to life. And those upgraded appliances? They're here to make your daily cooking experience a breeze. This condo offers a sweet outdoor space that's both secluded and private, providing the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Located in the heart of Greenbriar, this condo offers a very open floorplan with views of the 18th Fairway at Greenbriar Country Club!
